{"tid":953052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城教會鐵閘倒塌 女教友遭壓傷頭","createTime":"2018-12-23T15:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T16:38:33.000Z","uid":122068,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44cf040d007c3598fa10c6f06afdae31f7830df0","tid":953052,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"九龍城晚上發生閘門倒塌壓傷女途人的慘劇！晚上8時許，一扇重達過百磅、位於嘉林邊道一教會會堂的大門鐵閘突然鬆脫，壓中一名站在大門前的64歲姓吳女子，她血流披面，頭、面及眼部受傷，其69歲丈夫見狀報警求助，多名途人亦合力抬起鐵閘並將事主救出。救護員到場將她送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，現時情況嚴重，警員調查後將案件列作有人意外受傷，相信事件無可疑。至於涉事鐵閘雖佈滿血迹，但已立即被裝回，閘上亦貼上「請勿關閘」的告示。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\">女事主為該教會的教友，當時她返完教會</span>，正站在大門前等候丈夫，其間一道約4米乘2.5米的鐵閘突然塌下，將她壓中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181223/59063777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F59063777&d=TnS4iv0AzTN1VcoBQxMwhDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6d8f7139\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F59063777&h=9d9b880e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181223/59063777</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通呢個係上帝嘅考驗？"},{"pid":"9b5e2d7c9a449f08e92d3b82142cc67b16ebfc18","tid":953052,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"【23:39】傷者送院搶救後情況嚴重"},{"pid":"bbdd7faf3eea426456d51def3f8ee35438892e46","tid":953052,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"教友：耶穌我屌你老母"},{"pid":"7c9612f0737d0f66e25077c0ab74054e99e23974","tid":953052,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"如果植物人係咪每年大月教友去報佳音?"},{"pid":"eea22c13769481206856ebbf3a561ce8736dba88","tid":953052,"uid":135767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ee3ca57bc907ff68caf29b3bf71c641637b8db4","tid":953052,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"神做乜又考驗佢？"},{"pid":"e98cdaab5ad6e51085ed6d1d77e2180d5ba824eb","tid":953052,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"上帝要召見佢"},{"pid":"5976c75f0d4de95ceb2a5b8e14dbeb4e250757e4","tid":953052,"uid":12746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"呢個係神既旨意黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb8be43d10b22cf7ba1ed19826864af2b2040d8","tid":953052,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"蒙主寵召<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a15835ff0d5789dfc2deabe4a8568fbce233a5","tid":953052,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"耶蘇要召見佢"},{"pid":"489efe53b8519294ac7136e070a1fd3c1d3cd07e","tid":953052,"uid":168430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"神既考驗<br />\n不要問<br />\n只要信"},{"pid":"6f0497e5584a0f1762025593db811a1199053446","tid":953052,"uid":64093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"呢d 都係神既安排"}]}